OL,3,C'It makes you feel inhuman': Patient
OL,4,Creveals NHS corridor care ordeal
OL,6,FAn NHS patient who was left for more
OL,7,Fthan four days in hospital corridors
OL,8,Fhas described his treatment as
OL,9,F"inhuman".
OL,11,FPeter, not his real name, contacted
OL,12,FITV News after seeing our secretly
OL,13,Ffilmed footage of 'corridor care' at
OL,14,Fthe Royal Liverpool University
OL,15,FHospital.
OL,17,FIt comes as the Royal College of
OL,18,FNursing (RCN) warns it has become a
OL,19,F"permanent fixture" in NHS hospitals,
OL,20,Fwith some nursing staff describing the
OL,21,Fconditions as "a type of torture".
