OL,3,C'It makes you feel inhuman': Patient
OL,4,Creveals NHS corridor care ordeal
OL,6,F"This has got to be the worst
OL,7,Fexperience of my life," said Peter.
OL,8,F"It just makes you feel inhuman. It
OL,9,Fmakes you feel like you don't matter
OL,10,Fand as if they can just do what they
OL,11,Flike with you."
OL,13,FPeter, who was forced to spend his
OL,14,F60th birthday in a hospital corridor,
OL,15,Fsaid he wouldn't wish the experience
OL,16,Fon his "worst enemy" adding "it's not
OL,17,Fhuman and it's not right".
OL,19,F"It just makes you feel inhuman,"
OL,20,Fpatient Peter told ITV News
