OL,3,C'It makes you feel inhuman': Patient
OL,4,Creveals NHS corridor care ordeal
OL,6,FThe RCN has published a report warning
OL,7,Fthat collapsing care standards are
OL,8,Fpushing staff morale almost "past the
OL,9,Fpoint of no return".
OL,11,FNursing staff have shared shocking
OL,12,Fexamples of corridor care, including a
OL,13,Fpatient dying after choking,
OL,14,Fundetected in a corridor. Some nurses
OL,15,Fhave resorted to holding up sheets to
OL,16,Fprotect patient dignity when
OL,17,Fperforming procedures, and an elderly
OL,18,Fpatient was left to eat next to
OL,19,Fsomeone vomiting.
