OL,3,C'It makes you feel inhuman': Patient
OL,4,Creveals NHS corridor care ordeal
OL,6,F"I didn't go into nursing to deliver
OL,7,Fpoor care in poor settings. I wanted
OL,8,Fto make a difference and this is just
OL,9,Fembarrassing. People are being seen as
OL,10,Fnumbers and not as human beings.
OL,12,F"It's making me tired of working in
OL,13,Fthis environment and tired of nursing."
OL,15,F"People are seen as numbers," a nurse,
OL,16,Ffrom another part of the country,
OL,17,Fspeaking anonymously, told ITV News
