OL,3,C'It makes you feel inhuman': Patient
OL,4,Creveals NHS corridor care ordeal
OL,6,FThe RCN is calling for an urgent,
OL,7,Ffully funded action plan to eradicate
OL,8,Fcorridor care, including investment in
OL,9,Fbeds, the nursing workforce, community
OL,10,Fservices and social care.
OL,12,FLast year the government committed to
OL,13,Fpublishing data on incidences of
OL,14,Fcorridor care in England, but the
OL,15,Fstatistics still have not been made
OL,16,Fpublic.
