OL,4,Creveals NHS corridor care ordeal
OL,6,FA spokesperson for NHS University
OL,7,FHospitals of Liverpool Group said:
OL,8,F"Providing care in corridors is not
OL,9,Fwhat we want for our patients. The
OL,10,Fdemands on Emergency Departments are
OL,11,Fwidely reported and we are currently
OL,12,Fexperiencing significant pressure and
OL,13,Fhave to prioritise our sickest
OL,14,Fpatients.
OL,16,FIf you or a family member has been
OL,17,Faffected by this story, you can email
OL,18,Fus at healthstories@itv.com
