OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "No one should
OL,8,Freceive care in a corridor ` the
OL,9,Fsituation we inherited is unacceptable
OL,10,Fand undignified, and we are determined
OL,11,Fto end it. Staff, including nurses,
OL,12,Fare under immense pressure, and we
OL,13,Frecognise the dedication and
OL,14,Fprofessionalism of those keeping
OL,15,Fpatients safe and delivering the best
OL,16,Fcare they can.
