OL,3,C'It makes you feel inhuman': Patient
OL,4,Creveals NHS corridor care ordeal
OL,6,F"We have taken immediate steps to
OL,7,Faddress these issues including
OL,8,Finvesting #450 million to expand
OL,9,Furgent and emergency care services,
OL,10,Fexpanding vaccination programmes,
OL,11,Fpreparing for winter earlier than ever
OL,12,Fbefore, building 40 new same day
OL,13,Femergency care centres and 15 mental
OL,14,Fhealth crisis centres.
OL,16,F"At the same time, NHS England is
OL,17,Fworking closely with trusts to reduce
OL,18,Fvariation, tackle inconsistencies,
OL,19,Fimprove data collection and reduce
OL,20,Fdischarge delays, alongside social
OL,21,Fcare colleagues."
